# =======================
# CATATAN PRODUKSI:
# 1) Set KC_DB_TRUST_SERVER_CERT=false
# 2) Pasang sertifikat TLS server SQL yang SAH (CN/SAN = hostname yang digunakan Keycloak)
# 3) Tambahkan ke JDBC URL parameter seperti:
#    ...;hostNameInCertificate=sql.example.com
# 4) (Advanced) Jika pakai CA internal:
#    - Tetap gunakan encrypt=true;trustServerCertificate=false
#    - Impor CA ke JVM truststore di container Keycloak, contoh:
#        keytool -importcert -noprompt -trustcacerts -alias myca \
#          -file /opt/certs/ca.crt \
#          -keystore $JAVA_HOME/lib/security/cacerts \
#          -storepass changeit
#    - Mount /opt/certs/ca.crt via volume dan jalankan perintah di entrypoint/override.
